OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FThe GMB union has said if Asda loses
OL,7,Fthe case, they could end up paying out
OL,8,F#1.2 billion, as ITV News Deputy
OL,9,FPolitical Editor Anushka Asthana
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FA legal challenge against one of
OL,13,FBritain's biggest supermarkets that
OL,14,Fhas rumbled on for 10 years finally
OL,15,Freaches court today, as more than
OL,16,F60,000 Asda workers accuse the company
OL,17,Fof sex discrimination.
