OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FThe case against Asda, which claims
OL,7,Fthat the jobs of mainly women working
OL,8,Fon the shop floor are unfairly
OL,9,Funderpaid compared to predominantly
OL,10,Fmale warehouse workers, could have
OL,11,Fhuge implications for the entire
OL,12,Fretail sector.
OL,14,FThe GMB union claimed that if Asda
OL,15,Floses the equal pay case, the
OL,16,Fsupermarket giant could be looking at
OL,17,Fhistoric payments worth #1.2bn as well
OL,18,Fas an increased annual pay bill of
OL,19,F#400m.
