OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FIt comes after an email leaked to ITV
OL,7,FNews revealed that an independent
OL,8,Fexpert, who was commissioned by the
OL,9,Fcourt to compare the store workers'
OL,10,Fjobs to those in the distribution
OL,11,Fcentres, had concluded that the
OL,12,Fwomen's roles were of equal value.
OL,14,FThe findings, revealed in an email
OL,15,Fsent by lawyers Leigh Day to tens of
OL,16,Fthousands of claimants, appeared to be
OL,17,Fa major boost for the shop floor
OL,18,Fworkers.
