OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FThe case is being heard at the
OL,7,FManchester Employment Tribunal, with
OL,8,Farguments being made by Asda and the
OL,9,Fclaimants until November 22. A
OL,10,Fdecision is likely to be made in
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FIt comes after the retailer Next lost
OL,14,Fa similar case, where 3,540 workers
OL,15,Faccused it of paying shop workers less
OL,16,Fthan distribution workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
