OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FAlthough the tribunal did not find
OL,7,Fdirect discrimination, it judged that
OL,8,Fthe company had failed to show that
OL,9,Flower pay rates were not the result of
OL,10,Fgender-based discrimination.
OL,12,FNadine Houghton, GMB National Officer,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Asda workers had had to fight
OL,14,Ffor ten years, with bosses fighting
OL,15,Fthem every step of the way, just to
OL,16,Fget to today's hearing. They will not
OL,17,Fgive up now."
