OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FShe argued that "the entire retail
OL,7,Fsector has been built on the
OL,8,Fstructural undervaluing of women's
OL,9,Fwork".
OL,11,FShe said that if the court finds the
OL,12,Fjobs are of equal value then Asda's
OL,13,Fmajority owners - TDR Capital - should
OL,14,Fget around the table for settlement
OL,15,Ftalks.
OL,17,F"The new owners have loaded billions
OL,18,Fof pounds of debt onto ASDA's balance
OL,19,Fsheet - yet last year they reported a
OL,20,Fpre-tax profit of #180m," Houghton
OL,21,Fsaid.
