OL,6,F"TDR Capital was founded by now
OL,7,Fbillionaire, Manjit Dale - there is
OL,8,Fenough money to pay these women what
OL,9,Fthey are owed."
OL,11,FSusan Brierly, 69, left her home in
OL,12,FOldham early this morning to be at the
OL,13,Fcourt.
OL,15,FShe worked at Asda for 46 years and
OL,16,Fhas been a claimant for some years.
OL,18,F"It's been a long time waiting, it
OL,19,Fcould've been resolved," she said, as
OL,20,Fshe got ready to head out.
