OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We fully
OL,7,Frespect the right of current and
OL,8,Fformer colleagues to bring this case,
OL,9,Fhowever, we strongly reject any claim
OL,10,Fthat Asda's pay rates are influenced
OL,11,Fby gender. There are numerous
OL,12,Fdifferent jobs within retail and
OL,13,Fwithin warehouses.
OL,15,F"We continue to defend these claims
OL,16,Fbecause retail and distribution are
OL,17,Ftwo different industry sectors that
OL,18,Fhave their own distinct skill sets and
OL,19,Fpay structures."
