OL,6,F"Here I am, 63 years old, and I'm
OL,7,Fstill not getting equal pay, I'm still
OL,8,Fgetting treated like a second-class
OL,9,Fcitizen. I'm still having to fight for
OL,10,Fmy right as a woman, and that's not
OL,11,Ffair," she said.
OL,13,FMichelle Hunt, from North Yorkshire,
OL,14,Fsaid she felt "anger and frustration"
OL,15,Fwhen she found out about the pay
OL,16,Fdifferences.
